    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>2 same queries with uppercase and lowercase "and" operator</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>$sql = new \Zend\Db\Sql\Sql($dbAdapter);
echo $sql-&gt;select()-&gt;from('table1')
    -&gt;join('table2', 'table1.id = table2.table1_id and table2.field2', array(), 'left')
    -&gt;getSqlString();
echo $sql-&gt;select()-&gt;from('table1')
    -&gt;join('table2', 'table1.id = table2.table1_id AND table2.field2', array(), 'left')
    -&gt;getSqlString();
</code></pre>

<pre class="highlight"><code>SELECT "table1".* FROM "table1" LEFT JOIN "table2" ON "table1"."id" = "table2"."table1_id" "and" "table2"."field2"
SELECT "table1".* FROM "table1" LEFT JOIN "table2" ON "table1"."id" = "table2"."table1_id" AND "table2"."field2"</code></pre>

<p>Same to "or|between" operators.</p>

<p>Operators "in", "not in", "like" and others quoted a case-insensitive</p>

